      "id": "PopularPost339045",
      "post_content": "@DarkShinobi No one was confused about her only understanding 3 colours. What people (including me) are facepalming at is the total lack of subtlety in the flavour text. The other battlemages have flavour texts which give you some idea of what their abilities do and how they fit into their respective shards. Bant especially, as tenkaze pointed out, indicates the lack of knowledge regarding magical fire. They all require a varying degree of imagination from the person looking at the card.   \n  \nAll except Naya, who is basically whacking the reader over the head with it. \"HEY! HEY PLAYER! 3 COLOURS IS A THING! LOOK!\"",
